"1/3 cup loosely packed fresh rosemary leaves","1/3 cup loosely packed fresh oregano leaves","3 teaspoons lemon zest","1/4 cup kosher salt","1/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","1  (5- to 7-lb.) bone-in leg of lamb, trimmed","2 tablespoons olive oil"